    "description_long": "This object depicts a small graveyard scene set on a circular base with a misty, atmospheric backdrop featuring a full moon and bare trees. At the center is a single upright tombstone made of gray stone, flanked by two smaller gravestones. In front of the main tombstone lies a stone path, bordered by two white candles and a carved pumpkin with a green hand emerging from it, suggesting a Halloween or spooky theme. The ground is covered in a grassy texture with patches of fog, enhancing the eerie ambiance. The backdrop is a curved panel printed with a blue-toned, foggy forest and moonlit sky. The overall composition is compact and decorative, suitable for thematic urban displays or seasonal installations.",
